8%2581%259a%25e9%258a%2580%25e9%25ab%25ae%25e6%2597%258f%25e6%258a%2597%25e7%2588%25ad%25e5%258a%259b%25e9%2587%258f&h=064c86fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190718/s00001/1563460063337/%e3%80%90%e9%80%83%e7%8a%af%e6%a2%9d%e4%be%8b-emily-online%e3%80%91%e9%80%a3%e7%99%bb%e5%b7%b4%e6%89%93%e5%80%a1%e6%90%9e%e3%80%8c%e8%93%ae%e7%87%88%e3%80%8d-%e5%a4%a7%e5%ad%97%e5%8a%a0%e9%95%b7%e8%bc%a9%e5%9c%96%e5%87%9d%e8%81%9a%e9%8a%80%e9%ab%ae%e6%97%8f%e6%8a%97%e7%88%ad%e5%8a%9b%e9%87%8f</a><br />\n<br />\n噚日（17日）長者發起「銀髮族遊行」，以行動支持反對修訂《逃犯條例》嘅年輕人，證明自己並非「廢老」，感動唔少市民。今日有連登巴打提出，有需要拉攏銀髮族，提議設立「蓮燈」討論區，凝聚長者抗爭力量。<br />\n<br />\n為方便長者，呢位巴打建議討論區字體大3倍，背景變成最受長者歡迎嘅蓮花圖樣，而且每日會有不同嘅平安句子，例如「遠離警察暴力，祝願一家平安」。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>巴打仲建議「蓮燈」要有迎合長者口味嘅平台，例如「長輩圖台」、「養生台」；另有動員行動嘅「野餐台」，等長者加入抗爭行列，日後示威時，令警察更加警惕，唔會錯誤使用武力，誤打長者。佢話，其實長者過去傾向支持建制派，係源於缺乏別人關心，如果年輕人主動關心，兩代人溝通多啲，會對長期抗爭有好大幫助。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66928b27a559fca7af47b1a92ec57a2a12339e7e","tid":1331157,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T23:59:53.000Z","msg":"草船借箭：連儂見到720海報，唔使撕嘅，直接用marker將0改做1<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1331120\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1331120</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9b332bfafa0ecb4112fe9bff3f940f798b4a246a","tid":1331157,"uid":265521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T00:09:41.000Z","msg":"哇 咁勁"},{"pid":"9749c043becfe10d39bd5078202e0f028d2c9a66","tid":1331157,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T00:17:14.000Z","msg":"好人一世平安🙏"},{"pid":"57f5801d78be6c59feafbf2123b736c6a998184f","tid":13311